</ul>

<h2>Troubleshooting</h2>

<h3>Common Issues</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Hostname Resolution Fails</strong>: Check DNS configuration and /etc/hosts</li>
<li><strong>IP Detection Returns Localhost</strong>: Verify network interface configuration</li>
<li><strong>Permission Denied</strong>: Check user permissions for network operations</li>
<li><strong>Multiple IPs Detected</strong>: Review network interface configuration</li>
</ul>

<h3>Debug Information</h3>
<p>Enable debug logging to see:</p>
<ul>
<li>Detection method attempts</li>
<li>Network interface scanning results</li>
<li>DNS resolution details</li>
<li>Error conditions and fallbacks</li>
</ul>

